hyprsunset-qt: A small PyQt6 interface to manage hyprsunset profiles. It edits
hyprsunset-qt: ~/.config/hypr/hyprsunset.conf, fetches sunrise/sunset times for
hyprsunset-qt: your location, drops them into the day/night profiles, previews
hyprsunset-qt: temperature and gamma live over hyprctl, and restarts the
hyprsunset-qt: hyprsunset daemon so changes take effect.
